'''耶路撒冷圣经动物园'''（{{lang-he|גן החיות התנ"כי בירושלים על שם משפחת טיש}}，{{lang-ar|حديقة الحيوان الكتابية في أورشليم القدس}} ''{{transl|ar|DIN|Ḥadīqat al-Ḥaiwān Ūrushalīm al-Quds}}''）是一个[[动物园|动物园]]，位于[[以色列|以色列]][[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]，以饲养圣经中提到的野生动物著称<ref name="managers">{{cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/zoo-managers-from-around-the-world-go-biblical-in-jerusalem-1.353398 |title=Zoo managers from around the world go biblical in Jerusalem |last=Lis |first=Jonathan |date=1 April 2011 |accessdate=22 October 2011 |work=[[Haaretz|Haaretz]] |archive-date=2017-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929091938/https://www.haaretz.com/zoo-managers-from-around-the-world-go-biblical-in-jerusalem-1.353398 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根据[[邓白氏|邓白氏]]披露，耶路撒冷圣经动物园是2005年-2007年以色列最热门的旅游景点，2009年有738,000游客<ref name="attraction" />。

耶路撒冷圣经动物园由[[耶路撒冷希伯来大学|耶路撒冷希伯来大学]]动物学教授Aharon Shulov创建于1940年9月，位于市中心的库克拉比街<ref name="sbl">{{cite web |url=http://www.sbl-site.org/publications/article.aspx?articleId=579 |title=The Jerusalem Biblical Zoo |last=Greenbaum |first=Avraham |date=August 2006 |accessdate=28 November 2010 |publisher=[[Society_of_Biblical_Literature|Society of Biblical Literature]] |archive-date=2014-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140124202635/http://www.sbl-site.org/publications/article.aspx?articleId=579 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NY">{{cite web |url= http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=travel&res=9B03EFD71639F935A35750C0A965948260 |title=Jerusalem's Modern Ark |last=Kammen |first=Michael |date=6 March 1983 |accessdate=28 November 2010 |publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]}}</ref><ref name="NY" /><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://books.google.com/?id=hW_fAAAAMAAJ&q=Aharon+Shulov&dq=Aharon+Shulov |title=Christian Victory |volume=56 |year=1982 |publisher=The Company |page=6}}</ref>

